###################

Utility Keyboard Shortcuts

###################

-> Open terminal
Super + Return

-> App launcher
Super + d

-> Open Chrome
Super + w

-> Open Ranger
Super + n

-> Open Nautilus
Super + Shift + n

-> Open VSCode
Shift + v

-> Open Sublime
Shift + e

-> Launch Emacs
Super + a

-> Launch Github-Desktop
Ctrl + Shift + g

-> Launch Virtual Machine
Super + Shift + v

-> Launch Discord
Super + Shift + d

-> Screen Drawer
F3

-> Dropdown Terminal
F12

-> Launch Whiteboard
Super + Shift + w

-> Launch Chess-Game
Super + Shift + c

-> Quit Window
Super + q

-> Quit Focused Window
Super + Shift + q

-> Expand Windows
Super + Ctrl + {Left,Right,Up,Down}

-> Shrink Windows
Super + Ctrl + {Left,Right,Up,Down}

-> Lock Screen
Super + l

-> Reload BSPWM
Super + Shift + r

-> Quit BSPWM
Super + Shift + q

-> Reload Sxhkd (you need to do this after you modify sxhkdrc)
Super + Escape

-> Open Whatsapp
Ctrl + Shift + w

-> Open Telegram
Ctrl + Shift + t

-> FullScreen / Toggle-FullScreen
Super + f

-> Switch between tiled and monocle layout
Super + m

-> Swap current and largest window
Super + g

-> Switch to different desktop
Super + <number>

-> Send current Window to different desktop
Super + Shift + <number>

-> Move a floating window
Super + {left, down, up, right}

-> Focus the last node
Super + ~

-> Focus the last desktop
Super + Tab

-> Focus older node in focus history
Super + o

-> Focus newer node in focus history
Super + i

-> Launch Music Player
Super + Shift + m

-> Play Next
Super + F8

-> Play Previous
Super + F6

-> Pause
Super + F7
